## @ list.prefix.md

Term 1 (basic) with # -
: - Definition 1 # -
  - Definition 2 # -
  - Definition 3 # -

Term 1 (basic) with # - \*x\*
: - *Definition* 1 # -
  - *Definition* 2 # -
  - *Definition* 3 # -

<br>

Term 2 (basic) with # *
: * Definition 1 # *
  * Definition 2 # *
  * Definition 3 # *

<br>

Term 3 (basic) with # 1.
: 1. Definition 1 # 1.
  2. Definition 2 # 2.
  3. Definition 3 # 3.
